---
title: Loaded Beef & Pork Rice Bowl with Cheddar Cheese, Bacon Bits & Burger Sauce
description: Here’s a fun idea for tonight’s dinner, burgers without the buns! Let’s cook tender beef and pork mince in a flavourful tomato
sauce, and serve it on top of fluffy rice with some fresh and bright veggies. Don’t forget the burger sauce, this meal wouldn’t be
complete without it.

